Name: thealot
Version: 0.3.2
Summary: A lightweight IRC bot framework.
Home-page: https://github.com/nCrazed/TheAlot
Author: Edvin "nCrazed" Malinovskis
Author-email: edvin.malinovskis@gmail.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: TheAlot
        -------
        
        TheAlot is a modular IRC bot framework for Python3.
        
        Install
        ```````
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            pip install thealot
        
        Configure
        `````````
        
        .. code:: json
        
            {
                "server"                : "irc.quakenet.org",
                "port"                  : 6667,
                "channel"               : "#TheAlot",
                "nickname"              : "TestAlot",
                "prefix"                : "!",
                "database"              : "sqlite:///alot.db",
                "reconnection_interval" : 10,
                "plugins"               : [
                ]
            }
        
        Run
        ```
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            python -m thealot.thealot
        
        or
        
        .. code:: python
        
            from thealot import TheAlot
        
            bot = TheAlot()
        
            if __name__ == "__main__":
                bot.start()
        
Platform: UNKNOWN
